{
  "texts": [
    "This inflation strategy also provides a better initialization scheme.",
    "This is achieved by warranting I π (BA) = I d.",
    "The first column of B is set to ones, while the rest of the elements are randomly initialized.",
    "A[0, 0] is set to one, while the rest of the elements in A are set to zero.",
    "We refer to this variant as LoRMA π."
  ]
}